Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么Drift啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙 不管送多少过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都是赢不了我的废弃物的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.42,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21.79\pos(1224,571.5)}北方城墙被占领
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,获得胜利的人的将会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做无谓的挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:25.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地认输如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:26.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.92,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(945,823.5)\frz8.463\fs105\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&}结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:35.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,紫！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:41.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1734,109.5)}第四幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:41.95,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1635,217.5)}跃动的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:42.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把像你们这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:45.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从各个世界穿越过来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:50.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,称为漂流者 Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:53.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而另一类同样是穿越过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是人的邪恶之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:00.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们称之为废弃物 废弃者 ENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:05.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们十月机关看清了这点并进行监视
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:07.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后为了对抗废弃物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:11.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而把将漂流者集结起来作为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你们都不吃惊么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你说的东西我一点都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,十月机关的奥尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:27.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是有眼无珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然对着我这个举世无双的第六天魔王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:36.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是善 是恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:44.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁开始这么说的 我才是绝对的恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你又开始犯二了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得羞耻么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 还真是强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是原倾奇者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.23,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(897,9)}倾奇者：战国时代末期到江户时代初期的一种社会风潮。指好异风，着异服，行动超凡脱俗的人们。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们是哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:01.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该不会是废弃物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作为废弃物来到这个世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能够称之为人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:16.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只会一味地仇视 憎恨 怨恨这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:21.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道他们在你们的世界里面遇到什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:25.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们肯定憎恨一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到了不毁灭世界就不能消气的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃物来到这边要做的事情只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏杀戮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在北方集结驯服怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始向我们进军了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:47.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 他们会把这个世界破坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:51.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们想要借用你们漂流者的力量来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道怪物之类什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是敌人是有军队的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:04.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们十月机关握有多少兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是道士的结社而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是以集结漂流者为目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,劝说各个国家的王 领主让出军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再把军队交给漂流者指挥 指导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算世界不同 国家还是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:32.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,领主只有掌握兵权才能确保自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:39.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,支配者怎么会轻易把指挥权让给一些来路不明的人啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些废弃物什么的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他们再怎么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,领主也会紧咬着兵权不放的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那些 毁世之军 攻破最后的城池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:58.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要等到火烧屁股 切腹的那个时候才醒悟啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是所谓的君主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:06.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,春秋战国的墨家为什么会湮灭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管再怎么纸上谈兵 这一点是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:15.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 这就是织田信长么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是蠢货还是天魔 还真是令人无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有漂流者的话就赢不了他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那你说要如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:31.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者夺取这个国家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:38.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从现在开始要以这个丰久为头目开始夺取国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就来帮我们一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:44.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你们的世界的和平与幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我们来征服这个国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我来做老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,听都没听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前你可是坐在正中间的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:59.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是我想坐的 不过还是让给你坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那层意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是可怜的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 按我说的做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大师傅大人 事情变得很不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人完全不按常理出牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:26.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们的想法很有吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止曾有过几次废弃物们的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每次 这个世界都会负上极大的创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这次的废弃物与以往不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:50.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,若是用半吊子的方法就真的要被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个黑王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:06:02.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王大人 北壁卡尔阿迪斯已经完全沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯普京 损失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.81,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,9)}格里高利·叶菲莫维奇·拉斯普京，俄罗斯帝国尼古拉二世时的神秘主义者、沙皇及皇后的宠臣。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:10.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哥布林特战队274名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:13.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,狗头人前卫兵345名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:16.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,龙骑兵四骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:21.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然兵的减损比较少 但损失4骑龙兵还真是惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把负伤者集合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要医治他们么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是哥布林 还是狗头人亦或是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:42.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能救的全部都会拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是善良的黑王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王大人…黑王大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 战斗得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:28.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁沦陷这件事情散播出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:32.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 到现在还惧怕人类的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:36.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信人世要被毁灭的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都会来参加我的军队的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:46.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拯救人类 但是被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:52.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么拯救非人类之人就得把人类给毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是可怕的黑王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,追击逃掉的漂流者们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,追击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:09.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,追击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:14.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个道士会把他们带到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又打算前往哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他们集结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:25.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的敌人就只有漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:31.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放过一丝线索地搜索 发现 追踪 杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:39.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 跟着有趣的那一方走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会动摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:46.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,徘徊咆哮的不退之灾厄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,废灭人类的旅途是不会完结的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直到一个不剩为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:59.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以打倒最后一个为人之人为终结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:04.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以救赎所有非人之人为开端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,集结起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:15.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要给我停下 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:24.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要掉下去 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要干架么 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 都没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:06.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是把领主派遣的武官给杀掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:08.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有后路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是那个漂流者的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是会听那种借口的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:15.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且麦田已经有半数以上被烧没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有给领主的税了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:21.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,假如被原谅了 我们把所有收成都上供
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子就无麦可食了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经除了起义就别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我们说话期间 讨伐队就已经向这个村子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:36.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不理的话我们就会被杀死或者饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只能去打倒领主了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 没有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有的 有的 胜算是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:52.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要起义真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:57.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的信信 与一 丰丰都是很强很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行 完全不知道在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么可以和我们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:12.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我们作为魔导结社一直都在研究你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:17.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大师傅制作的这个便利的符术条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要贴上这个立刻就能交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的大师傅很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有这么便利的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道与一为了学习他们的语言有多么的辛苦么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不知道那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉啊 快给与一道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那么多 快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得太可怜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把术符拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,极东 日本国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,武士风的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我贴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:10.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:13.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 搞得他看上去像什么奇怪的怪物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:14.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好贴对地方啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和京都的阴阳师用的道符差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,十月机关的大师傅到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大胸眼镜妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫奥尔米 你只读对了O这个音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我这些长耳朵的家伙的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大抵能想象出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说得简洁点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:43.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是被称为精灵族的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,数十年前被人类的国家进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,败北后就一直作为农奴活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:54.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 妖精都是些怎样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 很长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:13:01.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有听说本来是自尊心极高的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,了解这些就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:09.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久快说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一旁说 你跟着我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就得让你来说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丰啊 要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要像刚才和我说话的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,先这样这样 然后那样那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个糟糕的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得被人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵 吵死了 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你们这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得羞耻吗 对祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:51.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得羞耻吗 对子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不想要国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想就这么卑躬屈膝而死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还是追逐志向奔跑而死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能不觉得羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能不想要国家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能想成为奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去夺取国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像「那个」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让人回想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要让我当大将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己来做不好吗 信长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要做在背后操纵一切的黑幕就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是你儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子已经在二条城死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被光秀杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是岛津丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是织田信忠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:30.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你一点都不像 你个呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别说无聊的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:50.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老爹还活着 大概也是这个年纪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是你老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,家久早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是织田信长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:06.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,萨摩？什么乡下地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么你个蠢驴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要打架吗你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这群人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想起过去了啊 兄弟打架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:30.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们哥哥十人都为平家效忠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一是为源氏效忠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就来干一架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:40.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}干吧 干吧 干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟有十一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:43.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是棒啊 还想再打一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,连弓箭都不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这样做的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定领主的军队正在逼近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是做这种事的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:09.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被他们杀掉的村长的儿子夏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟们受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是你们几个的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是什么「说不定」会来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:23.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是「肯定」会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:28.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们杀掉的巡查队没回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自然会集中军队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概要四天左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:38.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那群家伙装备不错 所以还会更快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是岛津的话隔天就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你们家太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群战斗民族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过怎么说都是后天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,离村庄的陷落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:56.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了 请帮帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有拿起武器战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:07.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,四十年前我们的国家被灭亡那时 我们还是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:12.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候奋起反抗的父兄们都被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连基本的战斗方法都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚他是不是说了什么奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 年纪多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,106岁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在日本可是会被当成怪胎打的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们两个多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,39
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,36
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大胸米 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫奥尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚刚开始就没打算记住我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不准抓我的胸啊你这色老头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,长耳精灵族是长寿的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:58.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是人类寿命的五六倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然生长也比较缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,比我年长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来这里就是精灵的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:13.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,却被来自东方的人类王国奥尔特占领
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:20.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他被毁灭的还有被称为矮人和霍比特等种族的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些种族的人民都沦为农奴矿奴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特现在自称为帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在占领地上施行着人类至上的占领制度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个奥尔特现在也在扩张中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正在东征西战中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:38.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然目前战线正陷入胶着之中 目前只是一进一退而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,理所当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺这事就是铤而走险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取国家后就只有两条路走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是将其彻底毁灭殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,或者让其像侍奉公主一样双手奉上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是四十年前的奥尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:00.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还有可以和黑王对抗的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的奥尔特…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:04.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这种半吊子的处理方法怨恨才会聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且已经过了四十年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:10.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像放任枯草就会引起燎原之火一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:13.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁都是满怀怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:17.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得昨天那群家伙要这样乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不杀鸡儆猴 就管不住他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是肯定会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀鸡儆猴肯定会来把你们杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要怎么办呢 丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢大将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识下岛津家的军法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:49.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把那群家伙都放进村里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太小题大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把一个毫无意义的小村庄摧毁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然需要两百名士兵 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:06.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉姆的巡查队似乎全部被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那群精灵哪里有这胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:13.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有传闻是被漂流者们杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被漂流者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:17.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者的话都是两三个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么强吗 漂流者…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人 这里一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根本空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:47.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 把那群家伙全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.28,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,把他们的头都砍下来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,-----ed------
